        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You instill within a creature the touch of the grave. For the duration, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Harm]{Harm}</em> and <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Heal]{Heal}</em> spells treat the creature as undead. In addition, harm spells gain a +2 status bonus to the Hit Points restored to the target.</p>\n<p>If the target wishes to avoid the spell, it can attempt a Will save to reduce the effects.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target heals half as much from <em>heal</em> and takes half as much damage from <em>harm</em> for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> Effects as described in the text.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The status bonus to the Hit Points restored increases by 2.</p>"
